<br>
Dont duel him in a large outdoor zone.<br>
<br>
Duel him in a noob dungeon you know well...blackburrow for instance.<br>
<br>
You see the XXXXX casts a spell message dive in water.<br>
<br>
Drag his pet off and kill it alone, or root it...<br>
<br>
If he insists on dueling inlarge out door zone, if he gets shadow step off and has a pet start running taking his pet with you.<br>
<br>
But the ideal is to whack him when hes not ready. Use some root poison,,,and pumice him before you strike to take off the damage shield.<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
